            Beyond Technology: The Human Impact
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Digital equity requires more than just apps and systems‚Äîit requires people. Our commitment extends to building digital literacy within communities that face the highest risk of disease and injury.
          </p>
         
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-6 border-l-4 border-blue-600 dark:border-blue-400">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">The Immersed ‚Äì Project Success</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Through the Immersed ‚Äì project, we empower individuals, such as young women and persons with disabilities, with the digital and health skills needed to access quality care and, critically, to act as health champions within their communities.
            </p>
          </div>
         
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="p-6 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-2xl text-center">
