        We believe in synergy. Our work is amplified by the support of distinguished global and regional leaders who share our vision for health equity.
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto rounded-full mb-16"></div>
     
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 group p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 rounded-3xl">
